title: Type3_Intron60 [10869X3]
characteristics_ch1: presenting symptoms (age at onset): Abnormal gait, frequent falls, difficulty climbing stairs, thigh pain (2y)
extract_protocol_ch1: Frozen muscle biopsies (~ 4 milligrams) were cut on a cryostat (20 microns) and homogenized with a 26-gauge needle in 400 microliters of 20 mM Tris*Cl pH 7.4, 150 mM NaCl, 5 mM MgCl2, 1 mM DTT, and 1% Triton X-100.  RNA was extracted using TRIzol® and precipitated with isopropanol according to the manufacturer’s instruction (Life Technologies).
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA (~1 microgram) was depleted of human cytoplasmic and mitochondrial rRNA using tiling oligodeoxynucleotides and the RNase H digestion method (Adiconis et al., 2013; DOI: 10.1038/nmeth.2483).  Illumina TruSeq Stranded Total RNA library kits were used to prepare indexed libraries.
data_processing: Single-end and Paired-end FASTQ reads were preprocessed using Trimmomatic for adaptor removal and with the quality filtering/clipping MAXINFO parameter set to 50:0.2 (Bolger, Lohse, & Usadel, 2014; DOI: 10.1093/bioinformatics/btu170) .
data_processing.1: Trimmed reads were mapped by the STAR RNA-seq aligner (version 2.7.2b; Dobin et al., 2013; DOI: 10.1093/bioinformatics/bts635) to the GRCh37/hg19 reference genome with splice junction annotations built using the basic 2-pass mapping strategy with known junctions from the GENCODE comprehensive gene annotation GTF file (Release 31lift37, https://www.gencodegenes.org) and novel junctions detected in the first pass mapping.  Sorted bam alignments files were filtered for secondary alignments and retained only uniquely mapped reads.
data_processing.2: The featureCounts program (version 1.6.5) was used to summarize the gene level expression values as integer number (Liao et al., 2014; DOI: 10.1093/bioinformatics/btt656).
data_processing.3: Coverage analysis used the BEDTools genomecov function with the UCSC bedGraphToBigWig utility.
data_processing.5: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: tab-delimited text file includes raw counts for each sample extracted by featureCounts
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: bigWig coverage files from bam alignment files for each sample
